<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>MovieRecs Home</title>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>Welcome to MovieRecs!</h1>
    <h3><em>The site that recommends your next movie.</em></h3>
    <br>
    <p> To start, please search up a movie or genre you like, we'll take care of the rest!
        You can add results to a pre-defined watchlist, or to one of your own.
    </p>
    <br>
    <br>
    <form action="/search" method="post">
        <div class="search-bar">
            <input name="search" type="text" placeholder="Enter a movie title or genre...">
            <!-- takes us to searchResults.ejs, might change to input type submit for post-->
            <input type="submit" value="Search!">
        </div>
    </form>
    <br>
    <form action="/viewWatchLists" method="post">
        <div>
            <!-- takes us to viewWatchLists.ejs, might change to input type submit for post-->
            <input type="submit" value="My Watchlists">
        </div>
    </form>
    <br>
    <hr>
</body>

</html>